All Classes

  • Class Description
    AllEventsResult
    This class handles the result of returning all events for all family members of current user
    AllEventsService
    This class returns ALL events for ALL family members of the current user.
    AllPeopleResult
    This class handles the result of returning all family members of current user
    AllPeopleService
    This class returns ALL family members of the current user.
    AuthToken
    This class represents an AuthToken that is paired with a user
    AuthTokenDAO
    This class accesses the AuthToken table and its data
    ClearResult
    This class handles the result of clearing the database
    ClearService
    This class deletes ALL data from the database.
    Database
    This class connects to the database
    DatabaseException
    This class extends Exceptions and is for exceptions occurring while trying to access the database.
    Event
    This class represents a big life event for a person
    EventDAO
    This class accesses the Event table and its data in the database
    EventResult
    This class handles results for returning a single event with specified ID.
    EventService
    This class returns an event object with the specified ID.
    FillResult
    This class handles results of generating ancestors
    FillService
    This class fills the database
    LoadRequest
    This class handles requests for data to be loaded into the database
    LoadResult
    This class handles results of loading data into the database.
    LoadService
    This class clears all data from the database and then loads the posted user, person, and event data into the database.
    LoginRequest
    This class handles requests to login
    LoginResult
    This class handles results for the Login API
    LoginService
    This class logs a user in and returns an AuthToken
    Person
    This class represents a person
    PersonDAO
    This class accesses the Person table and its data in the database
    PersonResult
    This class handles results for returning a single person object with specified ID
    PersonService
    This class returns the person object with the specified ID
    RegisterRequest
    This class handles requests to register
    RegisterResult
    This class handles results for the Register API
    RegisterService
    This class creates a new user, generates 4 generations of ancestor data for the new user, logs the user in, and returns an AuthToken.
    User
    This class represents a user of the Family Map App
    UserDAO
    This class accesses the User table and its data in the database
